      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive perfection. This 2020 Executive Sport Sedan is in showroom-fresh, mint condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating\u2014absolutely zero swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state; the premium Nappa leather is supple and free of any creases, and the interior still retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every surface, from the high-gloss carbon fiber trim to the crystal-clear digital displays, is flawless. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, featuring a complete, documented service history from the original dealership and very low mileage. It rides on a fresh set of top-tier performance tires and has never been driven in inclement weather. This is a collector-grade specimen intended for the most discerning buyer who demands a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
